### ==========================================
### Get All My Interests
### ==========================================
GET {{url}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### ==========================================
### Create Interest
### ==========================================
POST {{url}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"dealId": 1,
	"amount": 100000
}

### ==========================================
### Update Interest Amount
### ==========================================
PUT {{url}}/1
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"amount": 250000
}

### ==========================================
### Update Interest Amount (Minimum Test)
### ==========================================
PUT {{url}}/1
