Content-Type: application/json

{
	"amount": 1000000
}

### ==========================================
### Delete Interest
### ==========================================
DELETE {{url}}/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### ==========================================
### Create Duplicate Interest (Should Fail)
### ==========================================
